{"title":"瀑","authors":["李瑛"],"dates":[{"year":1994,"month":12,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"瀑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李瑛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你来看这年轻的大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这永不衰老的雷电和火焰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论太阳落下或升起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是飞腾着烟云雨雾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它们有时是花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时是群蜂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有时是星光或迸溅的血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你来听它的呼吸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那不息的奔腾和交响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"使人颤栗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时间，穿过拱形的大门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矢志向前，飞泻直下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有丝毫怯懦、软弱和犹疑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有刀刃般锋利的意志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以及力和美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对于这有声有色的存在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无论谁都不能不感到惊异"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你说它是一道飞瀑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就告诉你那是真正的悬崖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果你说它是一片风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就告诉你那是真正的生命"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九九四年五月二十三日于北京"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}